            "✅ Use batch_process_with_transforms() for batches",
            "✅ Access handler via integrator.handler when needed",
            "✅ Check dataset type compatibility for transforms",
            "✅ Monitor cache performance with integrator.cache_manager",
        ],
        
        "5. Error Handling": [
            "✅ Fail fast on validation errors (don't continue)",
